rComments: Prof. Misak really loves Pragmatism and it shows if you take PHL315. She was enthusiastic about the material and was helpful when it came time to have our papers done. I would take her class again in a heart beat. It was not a super easy course, but it was a fun challenge and I left having learned a lot. She uses her own book - it's a great resours

Professor Misak gives quite trying lectures, both herself and for students.  You get the impression that either she is trying to validate if what she says is making sense as she speaks, or her preparation for the class is suboptimal.  I personally like professors that provide readings online, but this course uses the textbook she authored herself
